Interface UbuduDelayedCustomEventHandlingAreaDelegate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    UbuduAreaDelegate

    public interface UbuduDelayedCustomEventHandlingAreaDelegate
extends UbuduAreaDelegate
    Extension of the default UbuduAreaDelegate interface. This interface allows to delay the decision of notifying user for event when custom handling the event.
